Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBQMInspection

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBQMInspection
public class JDBQMInspection extends Object
The JDBQMInspection class is part of a structure within the database which represents the SAP Inspection Lot hierarchy. This is the top level. Each Inspection has one or more activities associated with it.. The data is stored in a table called APP_QM_INSPECTION
